  Ester Sauter - Testing, EverQuest Live (Former GM Camii)<br>
  Anthony Garcia - Game Designer, EverQuest<br>
  Joe Russo - Game Designer, EverQuest(Former GM KaTavir)</font></p>
  <p><font size="3">ToyVault will still be in attendance and giving away their
  Iksar sculptor seen here!</font></p>
  <p><font size="3">The server sending the most players is The Rathe!! Karana
  and Cazic-Thule are running second!</font></p>
  <p><font size="3">The guild Divine Wind is sending the most members!!</font></p>
